::Zardus/DevilDuer/DeathStorm::

Zardus nods. "Very well. The CR chambers are down that hallway," He says, 
pointing toward the CR chambers through a hole in the base.

He turns to look at Nemesis with his one functional optic. "Did you get the 
newcomers?"

His comm-link suddenly plays back the message from Crow Lord. "No," he 
replies, "The longer the maximals and predacons are fighting, the better it 
is for us."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DevilDuer, Perndabot, and Bloodystrike walk off toward the CR chambers. 
DeathStorm follows, only pausing shortly to pick up Zergling and carry him 
toward the CR chambers.
